{"tid":1669914,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國金融時報指中國擬任命臨時行政長官取代林鄭月娥","createTime":"2019-10-22T23:31:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T23:53:49.000Z","uid":35790,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"69e7eca78b8b9e10f2f1ae79dd2629d555606312","tid":1669914,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T23:31:13.000Z","msg":"英國金融時報指中國擬任命臨時行政長官取代林鄭月娥<br />\n<br />\n23/10/2019<br />\n<br />\n        英國《金融時報》引述知情人士指, 中國政府計劃任命一位臨時行政長官, 取代現任香港特區行政長官林鄭月娥.<br />\n        <br />\n        報道指, 如果中國國家主席習近平決定<br />\n        推進這計劃, 將於明年3月前, 任命林鄭月娥的繼任人, 接替林鄭月娥直至2022年的餘下任期.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/default.aspx?NewsId=20191023053751\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2FNews%2Fdefault.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20191023053751&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=96ee4327\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/default.aspx?NewsId=20191023053751</a>"},{"pid":"d3bcb79e8b3e53e2244d2ba76fafed323636e1ec","tid":1669914,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T23:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d9860ac0852272015cdebcf6c0cd59d3a18b37","tid":1669914,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T23:32:15.000Z","msg":"唐唐大熱"},{"pid":"07576603ce753aba55c7785a4bf0828ad4143021","tid":1669914,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T23:32:52.000Z","msg":"亂放風je<br />\n唔存在法理咁做"},{"pid":"a77ca21be5ba82545b144ba3a271af3b76d7a109","tid":1669914,"uid":215876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T23:33:10.000Z","msg":"五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"f72b1b690458c21e356291337a261c40319ca457","tid":1669914,"uid":188374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T23:35:16.000Z","msg":"有我係度警隊都唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\